content.rendered:
Directed by Harish Shankar.

Written by Harish Shankar. A. Deepakraj. Ramesh Reddy.

Cast Allu Arjun(Duvvada Jagannadha Sastri ‘Jagannadham’ / DJ). Pooja Hegde(Pooja). Rao Ramesh(Royyala Naidu). Subbaraju(Royyala Avinash). Master Sathwik(Young DJ). Chandramohan(DJ’s uncle). Murli Sharma(Purushottam). Krishna Murali Posani(Home Minister Pushpam). Tanikella Bharani(Duvvada Subrahmanya Sastri). Vennela Kishore(Akella Vigneshwara Sarma ‘Vignesh’ ‘Viggu’). Harish Uthaman(Sultan Basha). Pavitra Lokesh(DJ’s mother (as Pavithra Lokesh)). Hari Teja(Lakshmi DJ’s elder sister). Rallapalli(DJ’s grandfather). Vidyullekha Raman(Katyayini). Shatru(Stephen Prakash, Naidu’s secretary). Sameer(Sameer Chandra). Shashank(DJ’s assistant). Sivannarayana(Venkatachalam , Vignesh’s father). Rajitha(Vignesh’s mother). Jeeva(Gangster). Prabhakar(Suri). Sana(Pooja’s mother). Sravan(DJ’s assistant). Vajja Venkata Giridhar(DJ’s friend). Joy Badlani(Central Minister) .Ananth.Kasi Bhatla.Devi Charan.Mozammel Hoshen Chowdhury.Jhansi.Roopa Lakshmi. Padmaja Lanka(Mother).Chandramogli Madem.Anitha Nath.Ramachandra.Pammi Sai.Gundu Sudharshan

Language Telugu.

Producers Ayan. Dil Raju. Sireesh.

Production Sri Venkateswara Creations. Goldmines Telefilms.
